    "Due to its usefulness across a diverse range of domains and applications, NER has become a core activity.",
    "NER is a key component in enhancing the capabilities of machines to interpret human language.",
    "It is challenging to perform NER in Indian languages due to a lack of resource [6], [19], [20].NER for Sindhi language would involve building a system that can accurately identify and classify named entities within Sindhi text.",
    "\"It's worth mentioning that NER for low-resource languages like Sindhi can be challenging due to the limited availability of annotated data and linguistic resources [2], [9], [16], [21], [22]."
